data.description: Welcome to this exquisite 4 bedroom, 3.5 bathroom townhome that effortlessly blends modern luxury with convenience. Nestled in the highly sought-after Bradley Square subdivision, this home is a true gem. No detail has been overlooked, as upgrades can be found throughout the property, elevating its elegance and functionality.  With its prime location, you'll enjoy easy access to nearby shopping centers and a host of amenities, ensuring that everything you need is just a stone's throw away. The townhome's layout is designed to maximize comfort and style, offering ample space for relaxation and entertaining.  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a harmonious fusion of contemporary design elements and timeless charm. The spacious bedrooms provide a peaceful retreat, while the bathrooms boast modern finishes and fixtures.  Whether you're relaxing in the cozy living area, preparing gourmet meals in the well-appointed kitchen, or hosting gatherings in the open-concept dining space, this townhome effortlessly accommodates your every need.  Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity as homes like this are in high demand. Schedule your viewing today and experience the epitome of luxury living in a convenient and desirable location.
